content:
Create and Assign a Learning Manager User Profile for Agent Engagement

You set up an enablement site (myTrailhead), created learning modules, and added the Omni-Channel widget to your org. Next on the agent engagement configuration list is creating and assigning a Learning Manager user profile.

Workforce Engagement is available in Lightning Experience and requires Enterprise, Performance, or Unlimited Editions.

To configure:

1. Assign permission sets.
	* Ensure the Learning Manager user has Workforce Engagement Analyst, Planner, or Agent permission set already assigned.
2. Create and assign a Learning Manager user profile.
	* Assign this profile to users who assign agent engagement modules to agents.
title: Configuring Learning Manager for Agent Engagement in Service Cloud
